sp.p:
We must of necessitie graunt that Peter was crucified vpon a crosse,Iohn. xxi▪
                   for so dyd Christ prophecie of hym, nowe, it is well knowen that it was the vse of the Iewes and not of the Romans to hange menne vpon the crosse. Wherfore I see not howe the people wyll beleue that Peter was kylled at Rome,


and put vpon the crosse by the Romans.
